 ♪<i> When we come together...</i> ♪

01:11:10.864 --> 01:11:12.567
A little higher.

01:11:12.567 --> 01:11:14.969
Good.

01:11:14.969 --> 01:11:15.470
Ow.

01:11:16.470 --> 01:11:17.470
One more.

01:11:16.470 --> 01:11:17.475
Seriously?

01:11:20.475 --> 01:11:22.609
 ♪<i> Can you feel</i>
  <i> The love tonight?</i> ♪

01:11:22.609 --> 01:11:25.613
 ♪<i> Yeah, uh-huh, yeah</i>
