♪<i> Maybe without</i>
 <i> A semblance of me</i> ♪

01:31:58.679 --> 01:32:03.284
♪<i> And not because you care</i> ♪

01:32:05.284 --> 01:32:12.627
♪<i> And you fall hard enough</i> ♪

01:32:13.627 --> 01:32:17.198
♪<i> You'll find</i>
 <i> Your heart is here</i> ♪

01:32:18.198 --> 01:32:23.837
♪<i> And then the grace</i> ♪

01:32:23.837 --> 01:32:27.108
♪<i> And then the glow</i> ♪

01:32:28.108 --> 01:32:31.377
♪<i> On either side</i> ♪

01:32:31.377 --> 01:32:38.309
♪<i> You might find</i>
 <i> The light below</i> ♪

01:33:02.309 --> 01:33:06.382
♪<i> And you won't be back</i> ♪

01:33:09.382 --> 01:33:16.756
♪<i> But one day
 This ache will fade to black</i> ♪

01:33:16.756 --> 01:33:17.158
Okay.

01:33:18.158 --> 01:33:20.261
I guess this is
good-bye, okay?

01:33:21.261 --> 01:33:23.265
I wish you could have gone
on the trip with me.

01:33:26.265 --> 01:33:29.229
I'll miss you.

01:34:20.119 --> 01:34:21.761
Shh, shh.

01:34:27.761 --> 01:34:29.104
I miss him, Dad.

01:34:38.104 --> 01:34:40.306
I just, uh,
hope he has a good home.

01:34:40.306 --> 01:34:42.475
Yeah. My kids
are gonna love him.

01:34:42.475 --> 01:34:44.475
Thank you very much.

01:34:42.475 --> 01:34:44.176
Bye. Thank you.

01:34:44.176 --> 01:34:45.878
Be safe.

01:34:45.878 --> 01:34:47.878
Hey.

01:34:45.878 --> 01:34:47.251
Hey.

01:34:51.251 --> 01:34:53.087
Let me know if you need me
to tuck you in tonight.

01:34:55.087 --> 01:34:57.859
Think I will.

01:35:33.859 --> 01:35:34.862
Mr. Bishop.

01:35:35.862 --> 01:35:38.268
Could you
please make sure
Jordan gets this?

01:35:41.268 --> 01:35:42.078
Thank you.

01:36:26.078 --> 01:36:28.617
Hey. How about giving
your old man a shot, huh?

01:36:30.617 --> 01:36:31.018
No way.

01:36:32.018 --> 01:36:34.018
Yes way. Your ball.

01:36:32.018 --> 01:36:34.221
Where'd you get that?

01:36:35.221 --> 01:36:38.490
I dug it out of the drawer.
This is my old one from 1990.

01:36:38.490 --> 01:36:40.327
Let's go. Come on.

01:36:40.327 --> 01:36:42.327
You ready for this?

01:36:40.327 --> 01:36:42.229
I'm ready for this.

01:36:42.229 --> 01:36:43.332
Let's go, old man.

01:36:45.332 --> 01:36:47.043
Ah! Dude, you pushed off!

01:36:58.043 --> 01:37:01.118
Ooh. You like that.
Yeah, that's a good one.

01:37:06.118 --> 01:37:07.021
Why are you always
spoiling them?

01:37:09.021 --> 01:37:11.490
Don't tell anybody,

01:37:11.490 --> 01:37:14.996
but I'm gonna miss a few
of these stinky things.

01:37:15.996 --> 01:37:18.636
I don't think
I'm a horse-ist anymore.

01:37:22.636 --> 01:37:25.238
I, uh...
I got your letter.

01:37:26.238 --> 01:37:27.408
Good.

01:37:29.408 --> 01:37:30.279
You sold Chief?

01:37:32.279 --> 01:37:34.050
Yeah. I did.

01:37:37.050 --> 01:37:38.288
But it was good for me.

01:37:42.288 --> 01:37:43.292
I finally did it, you know?

01:37:46.292 --> 01:37:48.564
Let myself be sad
about Casey.

01:37:51.564 --> 01:37:53.002
That's good.
I'm proud of you.

01:37:57.002 --> 01:38:00.573
Lee, that's a lot of money.
I can't accept it.

01:38:00.573 --> 01:38:02.443
No, it was Casey's.

01:38:03.443 --> 01:38:07.215
He would've wanted you to be
the first in your family
to graduate college.

01:38:09.215 --> 01:38:14.322
And you did that even...
even after I ended things.

01:38:15.322 --> 01:38:19.059
Yeah, well,
just because you don't want
to fight for us

01:38:19.059 --> 01:38:21.463
doesn't mean that I can't
still love your dreams.

01:38:24.463 --> 01:38:25.666
Well...

01:38:26.666 --> 01:38:28.436
it's enough for one year
at a state school.

01:38:30.436 --> 01:38:32.204
If I work hard enough,
I can afford the next.

01:38:32.204 --> 01:38:35.042
And if I get
good enough grades,
which I plan to...

01:38:36.042 --> 01:38:37.378
I could earn a scholarship
for my master's.

01:38:39.378 --> 01:38:41.413
You know,
statistically speaking,

01:38:41.413 --> 01:38:46.086
78% of minorities
with a GPA of 3.8 or higher
earn full scholarships.

01:38:46.086 --> 01:38:50.324
Wow. Sounds like
the math wiz has a plan.

01:38:52.324 --> 01:38:55.096
What about you?
What do you want to do
after you graduate?

01:38:57.096 --> 01:39:02.036
Guess I'll just stay here.
Give lessons, board horses.

01:39:03.036 --> 01:39:07.609
Hang with Ghost and Cody
until I finally figure out
what I want to do.

01:39:09.609 --> 01:39:13.145
Well, I missed enrollment
for fall semester.

01:39:13.145 --> 01:39:17.284
So I have to wait until
the spring rolls around.

01:39:19.284 --> 01:39:21.256
I have some downtime.

01:39:23.256 --> 01:39:28.060
And I figure there's
nothing else I'd rather do

01:39:28.060 --> 01:39:31.231
than get on a horse
for three months and...

01:39:32.231 --> 01:39:34.036
head towards
the Pacific Ocean with you.

01:39:45.310 --> 01:39:46.515
I missed you.

01:39:48.515 --> 01:39:50.418
I want to fight for this.

01:39:52.418 --> 01:39:55.122
Your broken dreams
are worth putting
back together too.

01:39:56.122 --> 01:39:57.231
Yes, they are.

01:40:06.231 --> 01:40:08.768
So, about those
toothless mountain men.

01:40:08.768 --> 01:40:10.837
Oh, my God!
You are still scared.

01:40:10.837 --> 01:40:13.773
I'm just worried.
I just think there's
power in numbers.

01:40:13.773 --> 01:40:17.773
That's all I'm saying.
Is that too much to ask?

01:40:13.773 --> 01:40:17.118
Yes.

