Thanks, Logan.

01:41:22.509 --> 01:41:24.444
Dad, you sure
you're okay with this?

01:41:25.444 --> 01:41:27.913
Yeah. I couldn't be
more proud.

01:41:27.913 --> 01:41:29.748
