everything you've done
for this family.

01:41:37.390 --> 01:41:38.757
Stop. Stop.

01:41:38.757 --> 01:41:41.757
Don't get mushy
on me, all right?

01:41:38.757 --> 01:41:41.161
Okay.

01:41:41.161 --> 01:41:42.628
You two need
to get on out of here.

01:41:42.628 --> 01:41:44.796
The trailer's already
packed, and I'll...

01:41:44.796 --> 01:41:47.699
catch up with you at your
first checkpoint tonight.

01:41:47.699 --> 01:41:50.336
Okay. Thanks for
running support, Dad.

01:41:50.336 --> 01:41:53.506
Yeah, I think
it was time for me
to take a vacation.

01:41:53.506 --> 01:41:56.876
This way, Logan and I,
we can have a little
road trip, right, son?

01:41:56.876 --> 01:41:58.279
Yeah.

01:41:59.279 --> 01:42:00.813
Seriously, guys.

01:42:00.813 --> 01:42:02.748
It means the world to me.

01:42:02.748 --> 01:42:05.220
Well, we want to be part
of your dream.

01:42:08.220 --> 01:42:10.457
-Take care of my girl.
-Yes, sir, Mr. Grove.

01:42:12.457 --> 01:42:14.493
-I love you, Dad.
-I love you too.

01:42:14.493 --> 01:42:15.895
Have a blast!

01:42:15.895 --> 01:42:19.666
Okay. I love you, Logan.
And I'll see you tonight, man.

01:42:19.666 --> 01:42:21.666
See you.

01:42:19.666 --> 01:42:21.970
Here you go.

01:42:23.970 --> 01:42:26.939
All right. Come on, bud.
Ready, Jordan?

01:42:26.939 --> 01:42:29.358
Ready.
Are you ready, Ghost?

